              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes"/>
              <para>
                <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM194794">Section 14(1)(c)</extref></citation> is amended by inserting <amend.in quote="1">or gas retailers (as defined in section 2(1) of the Gas Act 1992)</amend.in> after <quote.in quote="1">Electricity Act 1992)</quote.in>.</text>
              </para>
